edu.jhu.hlt.ingesters.simple

Class CompleteFileIngester

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.jhu.hlt.ingesters.simple.CompleteFileIngester
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Ingester, UTF8FileIngester, MetadataTool, SafeTooledAnnotationMetadata, edu.jhu.hlt.concrete.safe.metadata.SafeAnnotationMetadata

    public class CompleteFileIngester
extends Object
implements UTF8FileIngester
    Implementation of UTF8FileIngester whose UTF8FileIngester.fromCharacterBasedFile(Path) implementation converts the entire contents of a character-based file to a Communication object.
    • The file name is used as the ID of the Communication.
    • The Communication will contain one Section with one TextSpan.
